/-- If $A$, $B$ and $C$ are three collinear points in which $A \neq B$, then $C$ lies on the directed line associated to $AB$. -/
theorem pt_pt_maximal {A B C : P} [_h : PtNe B A] (Co : Collinear A B C) : C LiesOn (DLIN A B) :=
